WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:51.280 --> 01:53.360
I don't usually drink much.

01:53.920 --> 01:55.040
- So--
- Who did you go with?

01:58.040 --> 01:59.320
My roommates.

01:59.400 --> 02:00.800
They were all people I know.

02:00.880 --> 02:01.920
Roommates?

02:02.000 --> 02:04.280
What about the guy who came out
with you yesterday?

02:04.360 --> 02:05.800
The one who is 195 cm tall

02:06.600 --> 02:07.920
and just gave you a hamburger.

02:09.120 --> 02:10.360
Is he also your roommate?

02:10.440 --> 02:13.760
No, that is my roommate's
boyfriend's friend.

02:15.800 --> 02:16.680
Is that him?

02:19.520 --> 02:20.560
What do you mean?

02:21.720 --> 02:22.960
The guy you like.

02:23.520 --> 02:24.680
Is it him?

02:31.520 --> 02:32.400
Is he?

02:35.200 --> 02:36.040
No.

02:37.120 --> 02:38.160
No?

02:39.040 --> 02:40.080
So tell me.

02:40.160 --> 02:42.040
If that isn't your type, what is?

02:42.120 --> 02:43.000
I don't want to.

02:49.880 --> 02:50.880
Jiaxu.

02:50.960 --> 02:53.360
- The bubble--
- Is it a guy who is cute

02:54.840 --> 02:56.200
and delicate-looking?

02:59.520 --> 03:00.400
No.

03:02.040 --> 03:03.200
He…

03:03.280 --> 03:05.800
He's manly.

03:07.600 --> 03:08.560
Manly?

03:10.520 --> 03:11.360
So…

03:13.600 --> 03:14.760
You like

03:16.320 --> 03:17.240
muscular guys.

03:19.760 --> 03:20.600
Is that it?

03:23.000 --> 03:24.200
No.

03:25.600 --> 03:27.920
No muscles but is manly.

03:28.640 --> 03:30.360
Also, he's nice to everyone.

03:30.880 --> 03:32.440
But the guy you described

03:33.000 --> 03:34.840
sounds like a jerk.

03:34.920 --> 03:35.920
He's not a jerk.

03:36.000 --> 03:37.680
- He is.
- He isn't.

03:39.200 --> 03:40.920
You're so nosy.

03:41.000 --> 03:42.040
I'm nosy?

03:42.920 --> 03:45.160
I've never met a guy like that in my life.

03:45.800 --> 03:47.320
- Gosh.
- I'm just curious.

03:47.400 --> 03:48.440
You're so nosy.

03:48.520 --> 03:49.640
Can you stop asking?

03:50.120 --> 03:51.200
Fine.

03:51.720 --> 03:52.640
I won't ask anymore.

03:54.240 --> 03:55.440
If you're curious,

03:56.160 --> 03:58.160
just look in the mirror.

04:05.040 --> 04:05.880
Jiaxu.

04:07.560 --> 04:08.440
Yes?

04:09.520 --> 04:10.440
You…

04:11.040 --> 04:12.800
You're in your twenties now.

04:12.880 --> 04:14.520
Why don't you get a girlfriend

04:15.000 --> 04:16.079
instead of bothering me--

04:16.160 --> 04:17.519
Where would I get a girlfriend?

04:18.000 --> 04:19.079
Why don't you

04:20.880 --> 04:22.200
introduce one to me?

04:24.080 --> 04:25.440
That won't do.

04:26.040 --> 04:27.920
I only know girls around my age.

04:29.000 --> 04:30.280
Around your age?

04:34.680 --> 04:35.720
I'm fine with that.

04:43.360 --> 04:44.480
What do you mean?

04:45.640 --> 04:46.600
The literal meaning.

04:55.280 --> 04:56.600
Is he teasing me?

04:58.200 --> 05:01.200
He has never said
something like this to me before.

05:27.520 --> 05:28.760
Pull over.

05:30.000 --> 05:31.080
Mom!

05:32.360 --> 05:33.320
Zhizhi.

05:33.400 --> 05:34.760
Zhizhi.

05:34.840 --> 05:35.680
Zhizhi!

05:39.040 --> 05:40.320
I've missed you so much.

05:40.400 --> 05:41.360
You're finally home.

05:41.440 --> 05:43.200
What took so long? Was the flight delayed?

05:43.680 --> 05:44.840
No.

05:44.920 --> 05:46.280
It was Sang Yan.

05:46.360 --> 05:48.840
Sang Yan made me wait
at the airport for so long.

05:48.920 --> 05:50.120
Why?

05:50.200 --> 05:51.840
Why did you make Zhizhi wait?

05:51.920 --> 05:53.440
No, Mom. You told me to buy

05:53.520 --> 05:55.480
her favorite crispy taro-crusted duck.

05:55.560 --> 05:57.000
- Yes.
- I was in line for half an hour.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.360
You should've gone earlier.

05:58.440 --> 06:00.520
- That's right.
- You made her wait alone.

06:00.600 --> 06:01.520
That was so dangerous.

06:02.200 --> 06:03.720
My sweetheart. You've lost weight.

06:03.800 --> 06:04.760
I haven't.

06:04.840 --> 06:06.440
I made your favorite dish. What is it?

06:06.520 --> 06:07.800
- Steamed fish.
- Not only that.

06:07.880 --> 06:09.360
- I bought strawberries.
- Strawberries?

06:09.440 --> 06:10.480
Big strawberries!

06:11.320 --> 06:12.960
- White strawberries.
- Bring the luggage in.

06:13.040 --> 06:14.440
- I…
- Bring it all in.

06:16.520 --> 06:17.960
When the little princess comes home,

06:18.040 --> 06:19.200
I'm just a helper.

06:20.520 --> 06:21.440
The door!

06:29.920 --> 06:32.400
The little princess is home.

06:39.880 --> 06:40.800
Mom.

06:41.520 --> 06:42.920
Your New Year's gift.

06:43.000 --> 06:43.960
You bought it for me?

06:44.040 --> 06:46.160
You'll like it. Open it.

06:46.800 --> 06:48.040
Careful, this is hot.

06:49.040 --> 06:49.920
Is this it?

06:50.000 --> 06:50.960
Yes.

06:51.040 --> 06:52.040
And this too.

06:52.120 --> 06:53.200
You bought two.

06:53.280 --> 06:54.960
I saved up for a long while.

06:55.040 --> 06:55.960
Thank you so much.

06:56.520 --> 06:59.840
Dad, this is your New Year's gift.

06:59.920 --> 07:01.840
- Thank you.
- It's hand cream.

07:01.920 --> 07:04.040
Use it when you go to construction sites.

07:04.120 --> 07:06.360
Then your hands
won't get chapped during winter.

07:06.440 --> 07:07.520
Thank you, Zhizhi.

07:08.120 --> 07:09.640
- Good girl.
- She is so considerate.

07:09.720 --> 07:11.480
- I've grown up.
- Only she would think of this.

07:11.560 --> 07:12.720
I've become mature.

07:13.280 --> 07:14.120
Thank you.

07:14.200 --> 07:15.080
Don't worry about me.

07:15.160 --> 07:17.280
- Don't worry.
- You give her too much allowance.

07:17.360 --> 07:18.840
Stop funding her next semester.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.280
Where is mine?

07:22.880 --> 07:24.120
That's more like it.

07:24.200 --> 07:25.160
It looks great.

07:25.240 --> 07:26.960
- Really?
- Super cool.

07:27.040 --> 07:28.480
Mom, look at him.

07:28.560 --> 07:29.440
Isn't it?

07:30.080 --> 07:32.160
- What's wrong?
- What is this? I don't want it. Take it.

07:32.240 --> 07:33.800
Why not?

07:33.880 --> 07:36.040
- It looks ugly.
- It's not.

07:36.120 --> 07:37.840
I don't like it!

07:37.920 --> 07:39.480
Dad, does this look good to you?

07:39.560 --> 07:40.400
It's stupid.

07:41.920 --> 07:42.920
It's nice.

07:43.720 --> 07:45.040
I know you have a fine taste.

07:45.680 --> 07:48.680
Asymmetric glasses are trendy this year.

07:48.760 --> 07:50.480
- Don't you like it?
- No, I don't.

07:50.560 --> 07:52.520
- No?
- No.

07:52.600 --> 07:53.640
- No?
- No!

07:53.720 --> 07:54.560
Say you like it!

07:55.920 --> 07:56.800
I like it!

07:56.880 --> 07:58.160
Say you like it wholeheartedly.

07:58.240 --> 08:00.080
I wholeheartedly don't like it!

08:00.160 --> 08:02.920
- Then don't wear it.
- That's enough. I love this liveliness.

08:03.000 --> 08:04.240
Eat this.

08:04.320 --> 08:05.840
- Sit.
- Doesn't it taste good?

08:08.720 --> 08:10.000
Little demon.

08:10.080 --> 08:11.080
Let me tell you.

08:11.160 --> 08:13.160
I waited in line for half an hour

08:13.240 --> 08:15.400
to buy this crispy taro-crusted duck.

08:15.480 --> 08:17.600
You had better eat it and…

08:17.680 --> 08:19.120
Thank you, Sang Yan.

08:19.200 --> 08:20.840
Give my glasses back to me.

08:20.920 --> 08:22.680
I'll take them since they're free.

08:32.440 --> 08:33.360
Does it taste good?

08:35.039 --> 08:36.000
Zhizhi.

08:36.919 --> 08:38.159
Last time, you told me

08:38.240 --> 08:39.640
that Xiaoduan had appendicitis.

08:39.720 --> 08:41.280
How is he now?

08:42.200 --> 08:43.480
He has recovered well.

08:44.159 --> 08:46.640
The doctor said it was caused
by irregular meal timings.

08:46.720 --> 08:48.200
He didn't eat properly.

08:48.280 --> 08:49.280
So you heard that too.

08:49.360 --> 08:50.280
You mustn't skip meals.

08:51.240 --> 08:53.400
He had a tough life before.

08:53.480 --> 08:54.440
He was often working.

08:54.520 --> 08:56.800
That probably impacted his health.

08:56.880 --> 08:58.000
How is he doing at work now?

08:59.760 --> 09:01.360
Pretty well.

09:01.440 --> 09:03.960
Many of my classmates know
about the game he designed.

09:04.040 --> 09:05.600
It's very popular.

09:05.680 --> 09:06.800
That's good to hear.

09:06.880 --> 09:08.560
The boy is pretty good.

09:10.760 --> 09:12.360
Look at Sang Yan. He looks dumb.

09:17.400 --> 09:19.280
Listen, Sang Yan.

09:19.360 --> 09:20.400
Look at Xiaoduan,

09:20.480 --> 09:21.360
then look at yourself.

09:22.600 --> 09:25.080
I set up a meeting for you
and Mrs. Zhang's daughter.

09:25.160 --> 09:27.640
She waited for you all afternoon
and you didn't show up.

09:29.000 --> 09:30.440
I told you.

09:30.520 --> 09:31.760
I wouldn't go.

09:31.840 --> 09:34.080
I set it up for you. Why didn't you go?

09:34.160 --> 09:36.360
You should've turned up out of courtesy

09:36.440 --> 09:37.800
and met with her.

09:37.880 --> 09:39.440
Dad, Mom.

09:40.080 --> 09:42.000
Do I look like I need that?

09:43.040 --> 09:44.320
Absolutely not.

09:44.400 --> 09:45.840
So stop setting up meetings.

09:45.920 --> 09:47.280
I won't go.

09:48.240 --> 09:49.360
Was it a blind date?

09:51.960 --> 09:52.880
Fine.

09:53.800 --> 09:55.800
I've poked my meddling nose.

09:56.520 --> 09:58.920
You're always doing nothing all day.

09:59.000 --> 10:00.800
I thought you would have time for tea.

10:03.440 --> 10:04.760
I didn't know you were so busy.

10:06.120 --> 10:07.000
That was close.

10:08.960 --> 10:10.200
You're so stubborn.

10:10.280 --> 10:11.440
You'll end up old and alone.

10:14.560 --> 10:16.320
Enough. Don't waste the strawberries.

10:16.400 --> 10:18.360
I find that we've lost our dynamic.

10:18.440 --> 10:19.520
I'll toss one. Open wide.

10:20.480 --> 10:21.640
Don't waste the strawberries.

10:22.680 --> 10:25.040
- Zhizhi, this steamed fish is for you.
- I'll toss the bowl.

10:25.680 --> 10:27.640
Zhizhi, I made this steamed fish for you.

10:27.720 --> 10:29.120
Hurry and eat.

10:29.200 --> 10:30.240
Come on. It will get cold.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.240
- Okay.
- Hurry and eat.

10:31.320 --> 10:32.160
Come on.

10:42.200 --> 10:44.200
I don't need this. Put it back.

10:44.680 --> 10:45.560
I don't need this!

10:49.920 --> 10:51.200
Are you trying to kill me?

10:52.480 --> 10:53.680
Put it away.

10:58.800 --> 10:59.680
What's wrong with you?

11:00.600 --> 11:01.600
You must want something.

11:07.160 --> 11:09.760
Are you going on blind dates?

11:09.840 --> 11:11.520
Why do you care?

11:14.480 --> 11:17.320
No wonder you're suddenly so kind to me.

11:20.320 --> 11:22.560
So did you not go on that blind date?

11:24.800 --> 11:27.320
Do you think I need to go on a blind date?

11:27.880 --> 11:29.480
Don't you need to?

11:30.480 --> 11:32.200
What will you do
with the rest of your life

11:32.280 --> 11:33.760
if you don't go on blind dates?

11:36.920 --> 11:40.000
Was it because you felt embarrassed to go?

11:41.040 --> 11:42.640
If you do feel that way,

11:42.720 --> 11:43.720
you can

11:44.800 --> 11:46.520
ask Duan Jiaxu to go with you.

11:54.920 --> 11:56.520
Take him with you.

11:57.480 --> 11:58.640
You're single.

11:58.720 --> 12:00.240
He's one year older than you

12:00.320 --> 12:01.640
and he's single too.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.760
Besides…

12:03.520 --> 12:05.680
Besides, I think he may

12:07.320 --> 12:09.720
want a girlfriend now.

12:10.280 --> 12:11.920
Maybe you can go to him in Yihe.

12:12.840 --> 12:15.000
Or he can come to you in Nanwu.

12:15.080 --> 12:16.600
You two can go together.

12:16.680 --> 12:18.560
Then you won't feel embarrassed.

12:22.920 --> 12:24.200
Why?

12:24.280 --> 12:25.760
Did Duan Jiaxu get on your wrong side?

12:26.680 --> 12:27.640
I just think

12:28.720 --> 12:30.120
that he's not young anymore.

12:30.680 --> 12:32.760
If he doesn't find a girlfriend, he might

12:33.360 --> 12:34.640
end up being pathetically alone.

12:35.600 --> 12:37.400
If he ends up pathetically alone,

12:37.480 --> 12:38.760
that's his business.

12:39.400 --> 12:41.160
Don't compare me with him.

12:43.360 --> 12:45.200
So are you going on blind dates or not?

12:45.280 --> 12:46.120
I don't need to.

12:49.000 --> 12:50.840
In that case…

12:51.600 --> 12:53.320
But Mom told you to go.

12:59.360 --> 13:00.280
Do you know why?

13:03.400 --> 13:04.840
Because there's a girl

13:04.920 --> 13:06.320
trying to pursue me right now.

13:06.400 --> 13:07.360
Got it?

13:16.640 --> 13:18.160
What's with that look? I mean it.

13:18.920 --> 13:19.880
So…

13:21.360 --> 13:23.000
You can tell Duan Jiaxu

13:23.080 --> 13:24.800
to go alone

13:25.560 --> 13:28.280
and enjoy the blind date

13:28.360 --> 13:31.760
with his tacky pickup lines.

13:35.040 --> 13:36.520
Open the gate.

13:36.600 --> 13:37.640
Open it.

13:37.720 --> 13:38.680
Climb over it.

13:41.000 --> 13:43.400
Open the gate! You're so childish!

13:43.480 --> 13:44.840
Call me handsome. Come on.

13:46.440 --> 13:47.560
Do it.

13:50.800 --> 13:51.640
You're handsome.

13:51.720 --> 13:52.880
Louder.

13:53.880 --> 13:54.880
You're handsome.

13:55.520 --> 13:56.400
Even louder.

13:56.480 --> 13:58.120
What's wrong with you?

13:59.600 --> 14:01.720
You're handsome. Open the gate now.

14:02.440 --> 14:03.720
That's the way.

14:05.520 --> 14:06.600
You're a good sister.

14:06.680 --> 14:07.520
Please.

14:07.600 --> 14:08.680
Handsome, my foot.

14:12.720 --> 14:15.360
Hey!

14:15.440 --> 14:16.680
I have to go out later.

14:19.800 --> 14:20.640
Mom!

14:21.320 --> 14:22.520
Mom!

14:25.040 --> 14:26.040
Zhizhi, smell this.

14:26.120 --> 14:27.680
Does it smell like the sun?

14:27.760 --> 14:29.200
Why would it smell like the sun?

14:29.280 --> 14:31.520
I've sunned the quilt all day.

14:33.720 --> 14:36.080
That's why I'm just making the bed now.

14:36.160 --> 14:37.040
All right.

14:37.120 --> 14:39.160
Go and get the teddy bear blanket.

14:40.920 --> 14:42.040
Is it still in the cabinet?

14:42.120 --> 14:43.440
Yes, it's in there.

14:43.520 --> 14:44.360
Okay.

14:57.840 --> 14:59.160
- Found it?
- Yes.

15:04.160 --> 15:05.960
- I'll put it here.
- I'll do it.

15:06.040 --> 15:07.600
Mom, go and get some rest.

15:07.680 --> 15:08.520
It's late now.

15:08.600 --> 15:10.280
- Good night.
- Good night.

15:10.360 --> 15:12.040
All right. I'll go and wash this first.

15:12.120 --> 15:13.520
- Go ahead.
- Okay. Good night.

15:13.600 --> 15:14.920
- Bye.
- Bye.

16:04.400 --> 16:06.400
SANG ZHI, HAPPY 18TH BIRTHDAY

16:08.120 --> 16:11.440
SANG ZHI, HAPPY 18TH BIRTHDAY

16:23.640 --> 16:24.960
Where would I get a girlfriend?

16:25.800 --> 16:26.960
Why don't you

16:27.040 --> 16:28.320
introduce one to me?

16:30.120 --> 16:32.000
That won't do.

16:32.080 --> 16:34.000
I only know girls around my age.

16:35.080 --> 16:36.560
Around your age?

16:38.800 --> 16:39.920
I'm fine with that.

16:41.400 --> 16:42.840
Is he serious about that?

16:59.240 --> 17:00.080
SANG ZHI

17:00.160 --> 17:01.040
Jiaxu.

17:01.920 --> 17:03.920
I think Sang Yan has a girlfriend.

17:06.720 --> 17:07.640
Really?

17:07.720 --> 17:09.359
BROTHER NO. 2

17:11.520 --> 17:14.760
I think she's a younger girl.

17:15.520 --> 17:16.839
SANG ZHI

17:20.800 --> 17:23.040
Don't tell me he likes a minor.

17:26.800 --> 17:28.359
Is it fine as long as she's an adult?

17:40.040 --> 17:42.440
An adult would be in college.

17:42.520 --> 17:43.920
Doesn't that make her a grown-up?

17:46.320 --> 17:47.400
So why not?

17:58.920 --> 18:02.880
She's only asking about Sang Yan, right?

18:06.280 --> 18:09.000
It's acceptable when it happens
to someone else.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.560
But if it were to happen to herself,

18:12.120 --> 18:13.960
she would probably find it hard to accept.

18:15.040 --> 18:16.400
After all, to her,

18:17.040 --> 18:18.480
I'm just a big brother.

18:23.040 --> 18:25.120
Had we not met each other until now,

18:25.200 --> 18:27.320
I at 19 and he at 24,

18:28.840 --> 18:31.560
he would've seen me as a peer.

18:33.680 --> 18:35.240
Sadly, that didn't happen.

18:36.640 --> 18:37.880
Perhaps in his eyes,

18:39.640 --> 18:41.360
I will always be a 14-year-old girl

18:43.600 --> 18:45.760
who is just his good friend's sister.

18:47.120 --> 18:52.800
DON'T TELL ME HE LIKES A MINOR.
IS IT FINE AS LONG AS SHE'S AN ADULT?

19:09.040 --> 19:11.480
CHAPTER 13, FEEL YOU OUT

19:11.560 --> 19:13.800
I'M GUESSING YOU'RE FALLING TOO

19:17.200 --> 19:18.920
I've been busy planning my wedding

19:19.000 --> 19:20.560
and also had to come to Yihe for work.

19:21.040 --> 19:22.040
If you hadn't called me,

19:22.120 --> 19:23.600
I wouldn't have had much to eat today.

19:24.160 --> 19:25.560
Then eat more.

19:25.640 --> 19:26.720
Order more if you want.

19:27.560 --> 19:28.800
I won't hold back with you.

19:31.720 --> 19:32.880
Listen, Duan Jiaxu.

19:34.240 --> 19:36.600
I won't ask you and Sang Yan
to be my groomsmen.

19:37.440 --> 19:39.320
Why? Do you have a problem with me?

19:39.920 --> 19:41.680
I have a problem with you and Sang Yan.

19:41.760 --> 19:43.000
Picture my wedding.

19:43.080 --> 19:44.800
If you, Sang Yan, and I

19:44.880 --> 19:45.800
are standing together,

19:45.880 --> 19:48.000
people might think
you're there to steal my bride.

19:48.880 --> 19:50.480
That's nonsensical.

19:51.760 --> 19:52.600
Duan Jiaxu.

19:52.680 --> 19:54.560
We haven't talked much
on the phone lately.

19:54.640 --> 19:56.120
Why haven't you contacted me?

19:56.200 --> 19:57.640
What has been keeping you busy?

19:57.720 --> 19:59.720
What else but work?

20:02.360 --> 20:04.760
You haven't mentioned
the girl you like lately.

20:05.360 --> 20:06.240
Let's talk about it.

20:06.760 --> 20:08.080
Nothing has happened.

20:08.160 --> 20:09.400
There isn't much to talk about.

20:09.480 --> 20:11.440
Don't keep mum. Tell me. I'm so curious.

20:11.520 --> 20:13.400
Please. What kind of girl is she?

20:16.960 --> 20:18.200
She's a young lady.

20:18.280 --> 20:19.400
She's a bit younger.

20:20.840 --> 20:22.080
You don't know her.

20:22.160 --> 20:23.320
What's wrong with being young

20:23.400 --> 20:24.800
so long as she isn't a minor?

20:24.880 --> 20:26.640
Pursue her if she's of legal age

20:26.720 --> 20:27.800
or I'll look down on you.

20:28.520 --> 20:29.640
It's not like that.

20:31.520 --> 20:33.560
I feel somewhat guilty about it.

20:34.120 --> 20:36.640
Guilty? Aren't you worried
that she'll get taken?

20:37.480 --> 20:38.680
That's normal.

20:39.800 --> 20:41.560
If she meets a good guy,

20:41.640 --> 20:42.800
I'll be happy for her.

20:44.120 --> 20:45.440
Does that mean

20:45.520 --> 20:46.800
she has someone she likes?

20:50.800 --> 20:52.680
This girl is impressive

20:52.760 --> 20:54.160
to take no interest in you.

20:54.760 --> 20:55.920
Duan Jiaxu, don't be sad.

20:56.000 --> 20:57.560
What kind of guy does she like?

20:57.640 --> 20:59.560
I'll analyze it and give you advice.
Tell me.

21:01.920 --> 21:04.160
Well, this guy

21:04.800 --> 21:05.760
is quite a flirt.

21:06.280 --> 21:07.920
He is a ladies' man and nice to everyone.

21:08.800 --> 21:10.680
He might even be a bit shameless.

21:11.520 --> 21:12.360
Isn't that you?

21:14.120 --> 21:15.280
Are you insulting me?

21:15.360 --> 21:16.240
No.

21:16.920 --> 21:18.240
Is there any chance

21:18.320 --> 21:19.560
that she's talking about you?

21:20.320 --> 21:21.640
Impossible.

21:21.720 --> 21:23.040
I've met that guy before.

21:23.120 --> 21:25.240
His image fits her description quite well.

21:25.880 --> 21:27.240
He's quite flirty.

21:27.320 --> 21:28.680
He's just a jerk.

21:29.720 --> 21:30.920
Maybe not.

21:31.640 --> 21:33.920
You see, one speaks contrary to their mind

21:34.000 --> 21:35.560
in front of their crush.

21:35.640 --> 21:37.320
When I was in college, I chased a girl,

21:37.400 --> 21:38.960
Wan Ling in Foreign Languages.

21:39.040 --> 21:40.720
I was her rebound when she had a breakup.

21:40.800 --> 21:42.480
When they got back together, she told me,

21:43.240 --> 21:45.360
"Qian Fei, what kind of girl do you like?

21:45.440 --> 21:46.640
I can introduce one to you."

21:46.720 --> 21:48.480
What could I say to her?

21:48.560 --> 21:50.520
I simply made up someone based on her.

21:51.800 --> 21:54.120
You made up a girl based on her?

21:58.400 --> 21:59.600
It's not very likely.

22:03.200 --> 22:05.080
But it's possible.

22:06.120 --> 22:07.280
Right?

22:08.160 --> 22:09.960
Listen, I swear to you.

22:10.040 --> 22:12.680
I haven't met many guys who fit
that description better than you do.

22:16.080 --> 22:17.240
Miss, I want to order more!

22:21.680 --> 22:24.600
Am I the guy she likes?

22:24.680 --> 22:26.160
Sir, what would you like to order?

22:26.240 --> 22:27.800
- Chicken wings.
- All right.

22:27.880 --> 22:29.440
- And this too.
- Okay, right away.

22:46.320 --> 22:47.440
I've arrived in Nanwu.

22:47.520 --> 22:48.560
See you later.

22:55.400 --> 22:56.760
Okay.

22:59.320 --> 23:01.240
Why did he tell me this?

23:09.520 --> 23:11.160
- Do I leave the red packet here?
- No need.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.320
They're waiting. Hurry over.

23:12.400 --> 23:13.640
- No?
- It's fine.

23:13.720 --> 23:14.640
- Come on.
- Let's go.

23:15.200 --> 23:17.120
What took you so long today?

23:17.200 --> 23:18.200
The traffic was terrible.

23:18.280 --> 23:20.280
Listen, Qian Fei is really nervous.

23:25.440 --> 23:26.400
Buddy!

23:26.480 --> 23:27.720
Did you put on weight?

23:27.800 --> 23:29.040
- A little.
- Not much.

23:29.120 --> 23:30.080
Good, you're happy.

23:30.880 --> 23:33.000
- Hi, Sang Zhi.
- Qian Fei.

23:33.520 --> 23:34.760
Congratulations.

23:36.080 --> 23:38.280
I stopped her
from giving a red packet at the door.

23:38.360 --> 23:39.880
- You won't accept it, right?
- Right.

23:39.960 --> 23:41.560
It's just a little something. Accept it.

23:41.640 --> 23:43.200
I can't. It's the thought that counts.

23:43.280 --> 23:44.160
No need for this.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.400
Please take it.

23:45.480 --> 23:46.600
No.

23:46.680 --> 23:48.600
You're so generous today.

23:48.680 --> 23:50.720
Am I? I expect two packets from you.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.320
Don't just drink by yourself.

23:55.400 --> 23:56.440
You and I are drinking

23:56.520 --> 23:57.920
after the wedding, all right?

23:58.400 --> 23:59.960
- Take your seats.
- Right, come on.

24:00.040 --> 24:01.400
- You'll sit here.
- Sit here.

24:01.480 --> 24:02.320
Let's go, Sang Zhi.

24:02.400 --> 24:03.440
- Sit.
- Look after them.

24:03.520 --> 24:04.400
- You sit here.
- Sit.

24:06.040 --> 24:07.520
If he doesn't want it, give it to me.

24:08.120 --> 24:09.160
Jiaxu!

24:09.240 --> 24:11.000
- Jiaxu, over here!
- Over here.

24:11.080 --> 24:12.240
What took you so long?

24:12.320 --> 24:14.560
I was going in circles outside.

24:15.080 --> 24:16.800
You cleaned up nicely today.

24:16.880 --> 24:17.800
He's handsome, right?

24:17.880 --> 24:20.120
Hey, man. Do you know what time it is now?

24:20.200 --> 24:21.520
You nearly missed my wedding.

24:23.280 --> 24:24.880
I was going in circles.

24:26.120 --> 24:28.440
- Okay, I'll go and get ready.
- Isn't that the tie I gave him?

24:28.920 --> 24:30.080
Do your best.

24:30.160 --> 24:31.400
- I'll get ready now.
- Go ahead.

24:31.480 --> 24:32.560
- Sit there.
- Leave it to me.

24:32.640 --> 24:34.200
- Come on, take a seat.
- Sit.

24:39.440 --> 24:40.560
You're so well-dressed today.

24:41.920 --> 24:43.760
Jiaxu, say something nice.

24:43.840 --> 24:45.520
I'll give you a red packet for New Year.

24:47.760 --> 24:49.640
It's hard to say something nice about you.

24:50.960 --> 24:52.800
Why don't I call you "darling brother"?

24:52.880 --> 24:53.720
Call me "brother."

24:53.800 --> 24:55.080
I'm fine with "brother."

24:57.320 --> 24:58.560
Darling brother.

25:02.480 --> 25:03.440
Is he drunk already?

25:05.040 --> 25:06.280
Who are you trying to gross out?

25:06.360 --> 25:08.560
Jiaxu, you two have become grosser
since university.

25:08.640 --> 25:10.080
Indeed.

25:10.160 --> 25:12.040
Darling brother, they're badmouthing me.

25:12.120 --> 25:12.960
Gross!

25:15.600 --> 25:16.720
This is mine now.

25:17.520 --> 25:18.400
Starting today,

25:19.000 --> 25:21.000
Sang Yan is my darling brother.

25:21.600 --> 25:22.920
Are you insane?

25:23.000 --> 25:24.240
Sang Yan, give in. It's okay.

25:24.320 --> 25:25.160
Sure, okay.

25:25.240 --> 25:26.800
It makes me cringe.

25:26.880 --> 25:28.360
I've got goosebumps all over.

25:28.440 --> 25:30.200
- Let's drink.
- Bottoms up.

25:30.280 --> 25:31.160
Brother.

25:31.920 --> 25:33.240
Don't call me that.

25:33.320 --> 25:34.640
Hearing that makes me sick now.

25:36.360 --> 25:37.280
Then…

25:37.360 --> 25:38.280
What?

25:39.680 --> 25:40.840
Did something happen

25:42.200 --> 25:43.200
to him?

25:43.280 --> 25:45.120
He seems weird today.

25:46.320 --> 25:47.960
I'll tell you what happened to him.

25:50.280 --> 25:51.440
Here.

25:51.520 --> 25:53.520
Yihe Psychiatric Hospital.

25:56.840 --> 25:58.360
Go straight there when you get back.

25:59.760 --> 26:01.240
Darling brother, you're so considerate

26:01.320 --> 26:02.800
to find a hospital for me.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.640
Man, stop calling me that. Okay?

26:04.720 --> 26:05.960
Why, my darling brother?

26:06.040 --> 26:08.360
Scoot over, Sang Zhi. Let's switch seats.

26:08.840 --> 26:10.960
I'm going to puke even before I drink.

26:11.040 --> 26:12.040
Sit over there.

26:12.120 --> 26:13.680
Okay? Please, I beg of you.

26:15.520 --> 26:16.760
What's wrong with you?

26:16.840 --> 26:18.120
Scoot over.

26:22.400 --> 26:24.360
- It has been a while!
- Maybe for you two.

26:24.440 --> 26:25.640
We just met up last week!

26:27.400 --> 26:30.320
- Next, let's welcome our groom,
- What should I say?

26:30.400 --> 26:31.840
who's plump from love's nourishment,

26:31.920 --> 26:33.680
but still looks handsome,

26:33.760 --> 26:34.960
Qian Fei,

26:35.040 --> 26:37.520
and his beloved bride, Shiwen!

26:37.600 --> 26:41.480
Let's welcome them to the stage!

26:45.800 --> 26:47.200
I wonder if the staircase

26:47.280 --> 26:49.320
can bear the weight of their love!

26:49.880 --> 26:51.480
Let's give them a round of applause!

26:55.120 --> 26:56.200
Come on, Feifei.

26:56.280 --> 26:58.000
Look at this sturdy staircase.

26:58.080 --> 26:59.880
It's like the path of their future.

26:59.960 --> 27:01.680
With each and every step they take,

27:01.760 --> 27:03.280
they walk their way to their happiness

27:03.360 --> 27:04.240
and stability.

27:04.320 --> 27:05.280
And this moment

27:05.360 --> 27:06.920
deserves cheering and applause

27:07.000 --> 27:11.000
from all of you!

27:12.880 --> 27:13.880
Qian Fei.

27:13.960 --> 27:16.040
You have grown so chubby from love.

27:16.120 --> 27:17.240
I know

27:17.320 --> 27:19.280
you must have much gratitude deep within.

27:19.360 --> 27:21.240
Why not take the mic

27:21.320 --> 27:23.000
and say something to everyone?

27:24.080 --> 27:25.000
I…

27:25.640 --> 27:27.760
First of all, thank you
for coming to my wedding.

27:27.840 --> 27:29.240
I never thought

27:29.320 --> 27:30.960
that I would get married so soon.

27:31.040 --> 27:32.200
I…

27:32.280 --> 27:33.560
I'm sure my buddies didn't expect

27:33.640 --> 27:35.360
that I would get married so soon either.

27:36.320 --> 27:38.000
I also want to thank my wife.

27:38.080 --> 27:39.840
My figure and height

27:39.920 --> 27:41.040
aren't a problem for her.

27:41.120 --> 27:42.640
Even someone like me

27:42.720 --> 27:44.600
can marry such a beautiful wife.

27:44.680 --> 27:45.560
I…

27:47.480 --> 27:50.040
Guys, I've got a wife!

27:50.120 --> 27:51.440
Well done!

27:52.880 --> 27:54.400
Help me take a photo.

27:54.480 --> 27:55.560
All guests,

27:55.640 --> 27:58.600
let's raise our glasses!

28:00.840 --> 28:02.160
What are you doing?

28:02.240 --> 28:03.160
Raise your glasses.

28:03.240 --> 28:04.480
Yes, right! Raise our glasses.

28:04.560 --> 28:05.720
Buddies!

28:06.440 --> 28:07.640
Eat and drink your fill!

28:07.720 --> 28:08.600
Cheers!

28:08.680 --> 28:09.920
- All right!
- Cheers!

28:10.000 --> 28:11.200
Let's count down from three

28:11.280 --> 28:12.720
and wish them a happy marriage!

28:12.800 --> 28:14.720
Three, two, one!

28:14.800 --> 28:17.880
- Have a happy marriage!
- Have a happy marriage!

28:17.960 --> 28:19.320
Cheers!

28:21.520 --> 28:23.520
Okay, as we watch the lovely newlyweds

28:23.600 --> 28:24.760
leave the wedding stage,

28:24.840 --> 28:27.320
this marks the start

28:27.400 --> 28:31.040
of Qian Fei and Shiwen's wedding banquet!

28:31.120 --> 28:32.400
- Come on.
- May all of you eat up

28:32.480 --> 28:35.040
- Let's dig in.
- and become as chubby as Qian Fei!

28:35.120 --> 28:36.080
I want this one.

28:36.640 --> 28:38.040
It's so close to you.

28:38.120 --> 28:39.080
Fine.

28:39.720 --> 28:41.320
You can have

28:42.120 --> 28:43.080
all the corn.

28:43.160 --> 28:44.760
WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY HI?

28:44.840 --> 28:46.120
Are you happy now?

28:49.400 --> 28:51.080
I can't take it anymore.

28:52.640 --> 28:54.280
BROTHER NO. 2

28:55.040 --> 28:56.360
Why didn't you say hi?

29:02.560 --> 29:03.680
Zhizhi,

29:03.760 --> 29:05.320
I bought you a chocolate cake.

29:05.400 --> 29:06.280
It's in the fridge.

29:06.360 --> 29:07.440
Remember to eat it.

29:12.160 --> 29:13.520
It's not important.

29:18.080 --> 29:19.000
Who is Zhizhi?

29:22.800 --> 29:23.960
Like you don't know.

29:24.040 --> 29:24.920
It's my nickname.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.480
Why doesn't your brother call you that?

29:30.160 --> 29:32.080
He calls me that occasionally.

29:32.160 --> 29:33.160
When I don't tick him off.

29:33.240 --> 29:34.760
Who else calls you that?

29:36.840 --> 29:39.160
My dad, mom, aunt, uncle,

29:39.240 --> 29:40.280
and eldest aunt.

29:41.000 --> 29:43.200
Those who are close to me call me that.

29:52.520 --> 29:54.720
And what's up with "Brother No. 2"?

30:01.320 --> 30:03.040
Brother No. 1 and Brother No. 2.

30:03.520 --> 30:05.120
Is there a problem with that?

30:05.200 --> 30:06.800
Why am I your Brother No. 2?

30:08.000 --> 30:09.160
You're older than Sang Yan.

30:09.960 --> 30:11.120
So

30:12.240 --> 30:13.280
one and two.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.440
Fine.

30:27.240 --> 30:28.840
How old is the guy you like?

30:33.920 --> 30:35.920
Why is he bringing this up again?

30:36.000 --> 30:37.200
Why do you care?

30:39.200 --> 30:40.160
Tell me.

30:40.680 --> 30:41.880
Is he in the same year

30:41.960 --> 30:43.520
and same school as you?

30:43.600 --> 30:44.440
No.

30:45.480 --> 30:46.840
Who else do you know?

30:49.000 --> 30:50.720
I know people outside of school too.

30:51.280 --> 30:52.480
How did you meet him?

30:53.040 --> 30:54.440
We met while we hung out.

30:54.520 --> 30:55.560
Where?

30:55.640 --> 30:57.400
A bar.

31:01.000 --> 31:02.040
That's not right.

31:02.640 --> 31:05.280
When you were drunk, you told me

31:05.360 --> 31:06.520
that you met him at a KTV.

31:12.000 --> 31:14.000
Did I say that?

31:15.080 --> 31:16.600
What did I say?

31:18.800 --> 31:19.680
Yes.

31:20.560 --> 31:22.120
We met at a KTV.

31:22.200 --> 31:24.920
I've met a lot of people,

31:25.480 --> 31:26.360
so I got confused.

31:31.760 --> 31:32.680
What's wrong?

31:35.320 --> 31:36.320
Nothing.

31:37.920 --> 31:38.920
I just think

31:40.600 --> 31:41.840
that Qian Fei is quite smart.

31:44.400 --> 31:46.280
What does Qian Fei have to do with this?

31:55.240 --> 31:56.520
How did you fall for him?

31:58.000 --> 31:59.280
Give me a break, please.

32:01.320 --> 32:02.440
Why should I tell you?

32:04.240 --> 32:05.520
- Look at him.
- Let's switch seats.

32:06.800 --> 32:07.720
No, I don't want to.

32:07.800 --> 32:09.080
- You…
- Sit over here.

32:09.160 --> 32:10.200
Just sit there.

32:11.280 --> 32:13.600
My darling brother, eat up. Have more.

32:14.520 --> 32:15.400
No way.

32:15.480 --> 32:16.920
You just sit there.

32:24.040 --> 32:27.680
WE'VE TIED THE KNOT,
A HAPPY AND LASTING MARRIAGE

32:27.760 --> 32:29.000
Top it off.

32:29.080 --> 32:30.000
What does this mean?

32:30.560 --> 32:31.600
Are you not drinking?

32:31.680 --> 32:32.960
Is this how you respond

32:33.040 --> 32:34.720
to your challenge five years ago?

32:34.800 --> 32:36.760
Let me have a bite. Quickly.

32:36.840 --> 32:38.400
I'm starving.

32:38.480 --> 32:39.480
Here.

32:39.560 --> 32:40.800
- I'm so hungry.
- Eat something.

32:40.880 --> 32:42.880
- Then we'll drink after this.
- All right.

32:42.960 --> 32:44.200
Okay, don't worry.

32:44.760 --> 32:46.360
- No problem.
- You didn't even take a sip.

32:46.440 --> 32:47.920
- I'll fill it up for you.
- Okay.

32:48.000 --> 32:48.880
Where is Qian Fei?

32:48.960 --> 32:50.200
He's seeing the guests off.

32:50.760 --> 32:52.440
They're such a sweet couple.

32:52.520 --> 32:53.760
My goodness. I envy him so much.

32:53.840 --> 32:54.920
Envious?

32:56.240 --> 32:57.760
Lift your head. What's wrong?

32:59.120 --> 33:00.400
When are you leaving?

33:01.880 --> 33:03.640
I haven't seen them in a long time.

33:03.720 --> 33:06.000
- I want to drink with them.
- Okay.

33:08.000 --> 33:10.160
Here. Let's drink until we drop.

33:11.160 --> 33:12.680
Sang Yan, give up.

33:12.760 --> 33:13.800
I'm heading home then.

33:13.880 --> 33:15.840
Sure. Go home first. Do you need a ride?

33:15.920 --> 33:17.440
No, I can go by myself.

33:17.520 --> 33:18.720
I really can't stand those two.

33:18.800 --> 33:20.280
- Good idea.
- Okay.

33:20.360 --> 33:21.600
Come on, guys.

33:22.240 --> 33:23.120
Let's drink.

33:23.920 --> 33:25.680
Jiaxu, I'm heading home first.

33:25.760 --> 33:27.760
Here, a toast to you.

33:27.840 --> 33:29.480
I'm leaving, everyone.

33:29.560 --> 33:30.960
- Goodbye.
- Bye, little demon.

33:31.720 --> 33:32.720
Be careful.

33:32.800 --> 33:33.760
Little demon.

33:35.120 --> 33:35.960
Bye.

33:36.040 --> 33:37.240
Don't drink too much.

33:37.320 --> 33:38.720
Don't worry. I'll take care of him.

33:41.280 --> 33:42.160
There he goes again.

33:55.240 --> 33:56.080
Sang Zhi.

33:57.800 --> 33:59.040
Why are you walking so fast?

34:00.320 --> 34:01.520
Are you leaving too?

34:02.320 --> 34:03.560
No.

34:03.640 --> 34:04.720
But it's late now.

34:04.800 --> 34:06.520
I'll drive you home in your brother's car.

34:06.600 --> 34:07.840
Didn't you drink…

34:10.360 --> 34:12.199
You were sitting next to me all night.

34:12.280 --> 34:13.560
Don't you know if I drank or not?

34:13.639 --> 34:14.960
I know you didn't.

34:15.040 --> 34:17.040
But you don't have to see me home.

34:17.120 --> 34:18.400
I can go back by myself.

34:18.960 --> 34:21.080
Driving back and forth is troublesome.

34:21.719 --> 34:22.639
Not at all.

34:24.760 --> 34:26.000
It might be troublesome

34:26.080 --> 34:27.040
if it were someone else.

34:36.920 --> 34:38.480
What? Are you giving it back to me?

34:39.960 --> 34:41.560
I'm returning the red packet

34:41.639 --> 34:42.880
to our Zhizhi.

34:47.440 --> 34:48.639
Wait.

34:48.719 --> 34:49.960
What did you just call me?

34:50.800 --> 34:51.639
Zhizhi.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.840
You said people close to you
call you that.

35:00.680 --> 35:02.360
You should keep this.

35:03.280 --> 35:04.880
Since you've called Sang Yan…

35:05.800 --> 35:07.920
You should get something for that.

35:08.640 --> 35:10.440
It's for Zhizhi.

35:10.520 --> 35:11.600
It's no loss.

35:14.120 --> 35:15.040
Take it.

35:16.520 --> 35:17.400
Let's go.

35:31.120 --> 35:32.800
When are you returning to school?

35:32.880 --> 35:34.200
Tomorrow morning.

35:34.280 --> 35:35.200
What time?

35:35.680 --> 35:37.040
The flight is just after 8:00 a.m.

35:37.920 --> 35:39.120
We're on the same flight.

35:41.320 --> 35:42.520
Tomorrow morning,

35:42.600 --> 35:44.160
I'll come and take you to the airport.

35:55.160 --> 35:56.160
Thank you, Jiaxu.

36:48.600 --> 36:50.040
I'll go inside then.

36:57.880 --> 36:59.040
It's your New Year's gift.

37:03.320 --> 37:04.320
Thank you, Jiaxu.

37:05.560 --> 37:06.520
Open it.

37:41.360 --> 37:42.680
Are these my initials?

37:45.440 --> 37:46.360
Do you like it?

37:55.880 --> 37:56.840
Well…

38:02.920 --> 38:04.080
Go in and sleep soon.

38:06.280 --> 38:07.120
All right.

38:08.480 --> 38:09.320
Good night, Jiaxu.

38:12.920 --> 38:13.920
Good night.

39:06.400 --> 39:08.760
A bracelet with my initials on it.

39:11.480 --> 39:12.440
What does that mean?

39:23.920 --> 39:26.440
